":"A_ibilN nawawiy~apN","text_ar":"اـِبِلٌ نَوَوِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";) and for this purpose are bruised, and sometimes mixed with barley, and then moistened: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"basiysapN","text_ar":"بَسِيسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawaApN","text_ar":"نَوَاةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is cut off in the circumcision of a girl."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, in TA, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eu*orapN","text_ar":"عُذْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) The name shows that this is the prepuce of the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clitoris,"},{"kind":"text","text":"the end of which resembles the end of a date-stone. But see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baZorN","text_ar":"بَظْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~awaY","text_ar":"النَّوَى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What remains of the place of circumcision of a girl after that operation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baZor","text_ar":"بَظْر"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the place of circumcision of a girl, which is what remains of her"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baZor","text_ar":"بَظْر"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mutok","text_ar":"مُتْك"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"has been cut off."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawFY","text_ar":"نَوًى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pieces"},{"kind":"text","text":"of gold,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"each of the weight of five dirhems."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jb","text_ar":"جب"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawFY","text_ar":"نَوًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"region towards which one goes"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in journeying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"whether"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"near"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distant;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place that is the object of a journey:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Kálee, TA:) [a traveller's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"destination:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"course,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"direction, that one pursues"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) in journeying and in acting or conduct: (TA:) see an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SarofN","text_ar":"صَرْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(third sentence), and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaqara","text_ar":"عَقَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". It is of the fem. gender. (S.) See an ex. in some verses cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayonN","text_ar":"بَيْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["M","S","K","TA"]}]}}